						November 08, 2006<br/>
						</div>
						<div class="contentListSummary">
						The same oils that fry potatoes are now fueling a rapidly growing number of diesel vehicles. So far, the technology has mostly been improvised. AME's Fokion Egolfopoulos will take the first close look at how to optimize it.						</div>


